------------------------------------------------------------------9546 1451
VR=52.102-27.75*X-0.30*E         0<=E<=30      rR=1.25, aR=0.60   9546 1451
WD=5.3243-9.4995*X+0.45*E        0<=E<8        rD=1.24, aD=0.55   9546 1451
WD=8.9243-9.4995*X-0.046*(E-8)   8<=E<=30                         9546 1451
